Players are given the freedom to scroll around the scene and use the zoom feature to search for the elusive cats. One of the great features of the game is that it doesn't penalize players for incorrect clicks, allowing them to freely explore without fear of making mistakes. Additionally, when players are left with only five cats to find, the game provides helpful hints to assist in their search.

One of the unique aspects of "Where is my cat" is that each playthrough offers a different placement of the cats, ensuring a fresh experience every time. This adds to the game's replay value and keeps players engaged and entertained.
